tu libra de carne,

968
01:51:51,438 --> 01:51:53,804
para vengarte,

969
01:51:53,840 --> 01:51:56,172
para satisfacer tu obsesión.

970
01:51:56,209 --> 01:51:58,302
O...

971
01:51:58,344 --> 01:52:01,472
puedes escoger hacer a un lado
tu venganza

972
01:52:01,514 --> 01:52:03,607
